<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<title>Data Integrity and Constraints</title>
<style>
body { font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 12pt; }
h2 { text-align:center; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.caption { text-align:center; font-weight:bold; margin: 8px 0; }
table { border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin-bottom: 16px; }
th, td { border: 1px solid #000; padding: 6px; vertical-align: top; }
th { text-align:center; font-weight:bold; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<h2>DATA INTEGRITY &amp; CONSTRAINTS</h2>

<div class="caption">Table 1.1 Authentication Constraints</div>
<table>
<tr><th>Module/Field</th><th>Constraint Type</th><th>Rule</th><th>Validation Point</th><th>Purpose</th></tr>
<tr><td>Email</td><td>Format + Deliverability</td><td>Must be valid, normalized, reachable email</td><td>normalize_and_validate_email()</td><td>Prevents invalid account/login entries</td></tr>
<tr><td>Password</td><td>Length</td><td>Minimum 6 characters</td><td>signup(), login(), reset endpoint</td><td>Basic credential strength</td></tr>
<tr><td>OTP</td><td>Temporal + Single-use</td><td>6-digit OTP, 10-minute expiry, marked used after verification</td><td>_validate_otp()</td><td>Prevents OTP replay attacks</td></tr>
<tr><td>OTP Purpose</td><td>Domain Constraint</td><td>Allowed values: signup, login, reset</td><td>request_otp()</td><td>Prevents misuse across flows</td></tr>
<tr><td>Admin Login</td><td>Role Constraint</td><td>Admin email/password must match configured admin credentials</td><td>_check_login_credentials()</td><td>Protects privileged access</td></tr>
</table>

<div class="caption">Table 1.2 User &amp; Account Constraints</div>
<table>
<tr><th>Module/Field</th><th>Constraint Type</th><th>Rule</th><th>Validation Point</th><th>Purpose</th></tr>
<tr><td>users.email</td><td>Uniqueness</td><td>No duplicate user email allowed</td><td>signup() + DB lookup</td><td>Ensures one account per email</td></tr>
<tr><td>users.name</td><td>Length</td><td>Minimum 2 characters</td><td>signup()</td><td>Avoids blank/invalid display names</td></tr>
<tr><td>users.password</td><td>Hashing</td><td>Password stored hashed, never plain text</td><td>hash_password()</td><td>Credential confidentiality</td></tr>
<tr><td>users.is_admin</td><td>Boolean Role Flag</td><td>Boolean role state only</td><td>User creation and auth response</td><td>Role integrity in authorization checks</td></tr>
<tr><td>Password Reset</td><td>Existence Constraint</td><td>Reset allowed only for existing non-admin user</td><td>/auth/forgot-password/reset</td><td>Avoids unauthorized admin reset path</td></tr>
</table>

<div class="caption">Table 1.3 Product Constraints</div>
<table>
<tr><th>Module/Field</th><th>Constraint Type</th><th>Rule</th><th>Validation Point</th><th>Purpose</th></tr>
<tr><td>Product ID</td><td>Format</td><td>Must be valid ObjectId for single/update/delete operations</td><td>get_product(), update_product(), delete_product()</td><td>Prevents malformed record access</td></tr>
<tr><td>name</td><td>Length</td><td>Minimum 3 characters</td><td>create_product(), update_product()</td><td>Prevents invalid product entries</td></tr>
<tr><td>price</td><td>Numeric Range</td><td>Must be greater than 0</td><td>create_product(), update_product()</td><td>Maintains pricing correctness</td></tr>
<tr><td>create/update/delete</td><td>Authorization</td><td>Admin-only operations</td><td>require_admin()</td><td>Protects catalog integrity</td></tr>
<tr><td>Media Uploads</td><td>Persistence</td><td>Files saved with unique names (UUID)</td><td>create_product(), update_product()</td><td>Avoids filename collision/override</td></tr>
</table>

<div class="caption">Table 1.4 Order Constraints</div>
<table>
<tr><th>Module/Field</th><th>Constraint Type</th><th>Rule</th><th>Validation Point</th><th>Purpose</th></tr>
<tr><td>user_id</td><td>Referential</td><td>Order linked to authenticated user id</td><td>create_order()</td><td>Owner consistency of order history</td></tr>
<tr><td>phone</td><td>Length</td><td>Minimum 10 digits</td><td>create_order()</td><td>Delivery contact validity</td></tr>
<tr><td>pincode</td><td>Length</td><td>Minimum 6 digits</td><td>create_order()</td><td>Address quality for shipping</td></tr>
<tr><td>items</td><td>Structure</td><td>Must follow OrderItem schema</td><td>Pydantic OrderCreate</td><td>Consistent order payload structure</td></tr>
<tr><td>created_at</td><td>System Generated</td><td>Timestamp generated by server</td><td>create_order()</td><td>Audit and chronological integrity</td></tr>
</table>

<div class="caption">Table 1.5 Payment Constraints</div>
<table>
<tr><th>Module/Field</th><th>Constraint Type</th><th>Rule</th><th>Validation Point</th><th>Purpose</th></tr>
<tr><td>Razorpay Keys</td><td>Configuration Presence</td><td>key_id and key_secret must exist</td><td>_require_razorpay_keys()</td><td>Prevents invalid payment initialization</td></tr>
<tr><td>amount</td><td>Numeric Range</td><td>Must be > 0 (paise)</td><td>/payments/create-order</td><td>Prevents invalid transaction amount</td></tr>
<tr><td>currency</td><td>Domain Constraint</td><td>Only INR supported</td><td>/payments/create-order</td><td>Gateway compatibility consistency</td></tr>
<tr><td>signature</td><td>Cryptographic Verification</td><td>HMAC SHA256 comparison required</td><td>/payments/verify</td><td>Prevents forged payment confirmation</td></tr>
<tr><td>order/payment linkage</td><td>Traceability</td><td>payment_id, payment_order_id, signature stored with order</td><td>Order payload + DB</td><td>Payment audit integrity</td></tr>
</table>

<div class="caption">Table 1.6 System-wide Integrity Safeguards</div>
<table>
<tr><th>Layer</th><th>Constraint Type</th><th>Rule</th><th>Where Enforced</th><th>Purpose</th></tr>
<tr><td>API Schemas</td><td>Type/shape validation</td><td>Strict request models via Pydantic</td><td>models/schemas.py</td><td>Rejects malformed payloads</td></tr>
<tr><td>Authorization</td><td>Token-based access</td><td>Protected routes require valid JWT user</td><td>get_current_user dependency</td><td>Prevents unauthorized operations</td></tr>
<tr><td>Error Handling</td><td>Controlled failure</td><td>Unhandled exceptions mapped to structured response</td><td>app exception handler</td><td>Stable API behavior and observability</td></tr>
<tr><td>Database Availability</td><td>Runtime check</td><td>Mongo ping before critical operations</td><td>Auth/order flows</td><td>Avoids silent failure on DB outage</td></tr>
<tr><td>Session Integrity</td><td>Client token invalidation</td><td>Invalid token/user clears local session</td><td>frontend api interceptor</td><td>Prevents stale/invalid session usage</td></tr>
</table>

</body>
</html>
